.TH LOA-SORT-BY 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
sort by \- Sort items by a supported field
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> sort by <title|author|type|year|pages|language>
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Valid sort fields are title, author, type, year, pages, and language.
.TP
Shows a sorted table without changing stored order.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> sort by title
.TP
alexandria> sort by year
.TP
alexandria> sort by language
.TP
alexandria> sort by type
